<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Basic Alchemy -->
  <RI_BasicElixirs.label>基础药方</RI_BasicElixirs.label>
  <!-- EN: In ancient times, there were various complex medical theories, but today, only the most effective formulas have been passed down.\n\nSome ancient herbs were brought to fringe planets by Cultivators, where research led to the unlocking of the Basic Elixirs workbench, Alchemical Furnace, and a small quantity of medicine.\n\nAfter research brewing and psychite feaf, can make Wort and some drugs at the elixirs workbench. -->
  <RI_BasicElixirs.description>古代曾有各种复杂的医术学说，而如今，只有最有效的药方被流传了下来。\n\n一些古代药材随着修炼者传到了边缘星球，解锁炼药工作台，丹炉和少量丹药。\n\n研究完成酿酒，精神叶等科技后，将可以在炼药工作台制作麦芽汁和部分精神叶制品。</RI_BasicElixirs.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Elixir formula -->
  <RI_Cauldrons.label>丹道妙方</RI_Cauldrons.label>
  <!-- EN: As an alchemist, learn how to sense the effects of medicine with Qi and extract herbs with Qi from a giant cauldron that is often difficult to navigate to make Elixir. -->
  <RI_Cauldrons.description>炼药师不仅需要精通灵气操控，还要能够驾驭那些常人难以掌控的巨大炉鼎。通过灵气导引与萃取，他们能够从药材中提炼出精华，炼制出具有神奇疗效的丹药。</RI_Cauldrons.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Elysium drugs -->
  <RI_ElysiumDrugs.label>极乐奇药</RI_ElysiumDrugs.label>
  <!-- EN: Once, alchemist adepts engaged in elixir refinement inadvertently created many substances with uncanny effects—some granting blissful euphoria, others casting users into endless, dreamlike stupor.\n\nThese drugs once flourished throughout history, bringing ruin to countless families, and were later universally classified as contraband. Regardless of intent, renewed research into Elysium drugs is believed to erode the true resolve of those who seek the Path.\n\nUnlocks Elysium drugs with special effects. -->
  <RI_ElysiumDrugs.description>曾经炼制丹药的方士集团，意外发明过不少药效奇妙的药物，或令人飘飘欲仙，或令人大梦不醒。\n\n这类药物在历史上曾经盛行一时，令无数人家破人亡，后来统一被列入违禁品。无论出于什么目的，对奇药的再次研究，不会打扰求道之人的本心。\n\n解锁具有特殊效果的奇药。</RI_ElysiumDrugs.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Medical herb planting -->
  <RI_FertileSoil.label>药材种植</RI_FertileSoil.label>
  <!-- EN: The planting technology has been further upgraded, and advanced medicinal herbs are now being grown on a large scale. Cultivators have also created a simple planting box for growing plants indoors. -->
  <RI_FertileSoil.description>种植技术进一步升级，高级药材被大面积试种。修士们还制造了一种简易的种植箱，用于在室内培育植物。</RI_FertileSoil.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Road to cultivate -->
  <RI_ImmortalStart.label>踏上仙路</RI_ImmortalStart.label>
  <!-- EN: You will embark on the road of cultivation—training, upgrade, and undertaking a series of adventures, ultimately ascending to immortal.\n\nBasic Cultivation Technology, unlocks the most fundamental cultivation facilities.\n\n*To begin Cultivation, a pawn must be implanted with a Spirit Root. Spirit Roots can be obtained through various means: trade, consuming Jade wine, or harvesting them from other Cultivators. Cultivators require a cultivation spot or more advanced cultivation facilities to train, and training tasks must be assigned to them accordingly.\n\nWhen the Cultivation progress reaches 100%, the Realm Transformation hediff will be applied. At this point, a upgrade can be attempted at the Upgrade platform. Be aware, if the upgrade fails, the Cultivator's meridians will suffer severe damage. -->
  <RI_ImmortalStart.description>你将踏上仙路，修炼，突破，展开一系列冒险，最终羽化登仙。\n\n基础仙路科技，解锁最基本的修炼设施。\n\n*想要开始修炼，必须为小人植入一份灵芽。灵芽可以通过各种方式获得：贸易，服用青玉仙露，或者割下其他修炼者的灵芽。修炼者需要一个修炼点，或者更高级的修炼设施来修炼，为修炼者安排修炼工作。\n\n当修炼进度达到100%将会有“境界圆满”Hediff，届时将可以在突破台上进行突破，注意，如果突破失败，修炼者的经脉将受到重创。</RI_ImmortalStart.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Cultivation path tree -->
  <RI_InitialApproach.label>法门树</RI_InitialApproach.label>
  <!-- EN: Cultivation Path is a shorthand for cultivation approach. It is said that since the earliest Celestial Master invented the method of cultivation, an increasing number of Cultivation Paths have emerged, but in truth, there are only eight original Cultivation Paths.\n\nDue to the significant differences in the Qi circulation logic controlled by each Cultivation Path, a Cultivator can only choose one Cultivation Path to follow. However, some elixirs can be used to forget a Cultivation Path.\n\n*To learn any Cultivation Path, one must first obtain a Cultivation Path Book. The Cultivation Path Book can be randomly acquired from Ruins Tomb quests, or obtained through events. A more reliable method is to build good relations with a large Sect and then summon a merchant caravan to make a purchase. -->
  <RI_InitialApproach.description>法门，是修炼方向的简称，自从龙师们发明修炼之法和法门，便有越来越多的民间法门诞生，但真正的原初法门就只有八条。\n\n由于不同法门各自掌握的灵气运转逻辑差异极大，所以一名修炼者只能选择一条法门进行修炼，不过，一些丹药可以用于遗忘法门。\n\n*学习任何一条法门，必须要先获得一本法门书，法门书可以从荒冢任务中随机获取一本，也可以从事件中获得，更稳妥的办法是和大型宗门交好后，呼叫商队购买。获得法门书后，必须在经书研究台上进行学习。</RI_InitialApproach.description>
  
